upreme Court Justice Clarence Thomas says his wife, Virginia, makes him \u201cwhole.\u201d\n\n\u201cIt\u2019d be impossible without you. It\u2019s sorta like, how do you run with one leg? You can\u2019t.\u201d\n\nGod bless Clarence and Virginia Thomas.", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 2561}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASZD09Q3t", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 29, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8534571, "raw_content": "When I was a younger man (\u201cthinking with the wrong head\u201d), I briefly dated your typical woke, far-left, hot-but-crazy female with dyed hair & tats while living in Portland, OR. \ud83d\ude2c\ud83e\udd26\n\nChecked her IG for the first time in years on a whim today; she just moved to Japan on a work visa, and of course made a long post shitting on America while praising Japan! \ud83e\udd28\n\nAlways blows my mind how they flee the outcomes of the policies that THEY voted for! \ud83d\ude02 \n\nJapan has the OPPOSITE of everything she vehemently supports; there\u2019s no multiculturalism, no promotion of queering, no welcoming of \u201cmigrants\u201d or muzzies. AND their PM *LOVES* Trump!! \ud83e\udd23\n\nWhy can they never put two and two together?!? \ud83e\udd21 Thank God she cannot also vote Japan into ruin, like they do when they flee their blue shitholes that they created in favor of red states (all while continuing to vote for evil/retarded politicians and policy.)\n\nPS: As an older and wiser man, I have since been blessed with a lovely, Christian, conservative, supportive, demure Filipina woman. \ud83d\ude2e\u200d\ud83d\udca8\ud83d\ude4f\ud83c\udffb never give up on love.. just AWLFs!\n\n", "author": "no_antifa", "created": 1775263865196, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "no_antifa", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Ex-girlfriend lulz", "last_comment_created": 1775273396297, "content": "<p>When I was a younger man (\u201cthinking with the wrong head\u201d), I briefly dated your typical woke, far-left, hot-but-crazy female with dyed hair &amp; tats while living in Portland, OR. \ud83d\ude2c\ud83e\udd26</p>\n<p>Checked her IG for the first time in years on a whim today; she just moved to Japan on a work visa, and of course made a long post shitting on America while praising Japan! \ud83e\udd28</p>\n<p>Always blows my mind how they flee the outcomes of the policies that THEY voted for! \ud83d\ude02</p>\n<p>Japan has the OPPOSITE of everything she vehemently supports; there\u2019s no multiculturalism, no promotion of queering, no welcoming of \u201cmigrants\u201d or muzzies. AND their PM <em>LOVES</em> Trump!! \ud83e\udd23</p>\n<p>Why can they never put two and two together?!? \ud83e\udd21 Thank God she cannot also vote Japan into ruin, like they do when they flee their blue shitholes that they created in favor of red states (all while continuing to vote for evil/retarded politicians and policy.)</p>\n<p>PS: As an older and wiser man, I have since been blessed with a lovely, Christian, conservative, supportive, demure Filipina woman. \ud83d\ude2e\u200d\ud83d\udca8\ud83d\ude4f\ud83c\udffb never give up on love.. just AWLFs!</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 10, "score_up": 29, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2040211158586548653", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "